title: eCQM FHIR Update 2025
description: This library is the final release version of the eCQM FHIR release manifest (also referred to as an expansion profile) that specifies expansion rules for the set of value sets used for FHIR-based eCQMs published for public comment review as part of the eCQM 2025 Annual Update.
purpose: This library is a release manifest that provides explicit version information for all the dependencies of FHIR-based eCQMs published for public comment review as part of the eCQM 2025 Annual Update.
